Package: alarm-client
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, yad, pssh, inotify-tools, ffmpeg, sshpass, ssh-askpass
Description: Notifies about emergency alarms and distributes them
 The package provides a system to be notified by alarm set of by Dash buttons
 and distributed by a properly configured AP (see alarm-ap package). For faster
 notification, the client helps distributing the alarm in the network. There is
 a tool for the local configuration.
